                "text": "The Vera Controller will now begin the un-pairing process."
              },
              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_4711_reset",
                "text": "1. Simultaneously press and hold the Up and Down buttons at the same time for 3 seconds to enter the advanced settings menu.<br/>2. Then simultaneously press both the Up and Down buttons once to select the Menu 1 (Z-Wave menu).<br/>3. Now press the Up button to select 'OFF'.<br/>4. Press the Up and Down buttons at the same time once to exclude your thermostat.<br/><br/>When your thermostat is un-pairing, 'OFF' will blink fast and the connectivity icon will be animated. 'OFF' will display solid (not blinking) to indicate that your thermostat has been successfully unpaired.<br/><br/>If unpairing was unsuccessful 'Err' will be displayed for 3 second followed by the 'Off' text changing to 'On'.<br/><br/>Click the 'Try Adding It Again' button to begin the pairing process."
              }
